<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Como você conheceu o Monogenius?</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/static/assets/img/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/static/assets/img/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/static/assets/img/favicon/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/static/assets/img/favicon/site.webmanifest">  		
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .bg-custom-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 font-sans">
    <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-xl rounded-lg p-8 max-w-2xl w-full">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Olá, <%= user.fname %>!</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Gostaríamos de saber mais sobre como você chegou até o <span class="font-semibold">Monogenius</span>:</p>
            </div>
            
            <form action="/survey/user-source" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <label for="sourceOfKnowledge" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Como você conheceu o Monogenius?</label>
                    <select name="sourceOfKnowledge" id="sourceOfKnowledge" required class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500">
                        <option value="">Selecione uma opção</option>
                        <option value="WhatsApp">WhatsApp</option>
                        <option value="Recomendação de amigo">Recomendação de amigo</option>
                        <option value="Facebook">Facebook</option>
                        <option value="Instagram">Instagram</option>
                        <option value="Google">Pesquisa no Google</option>
                        <option value="Email">Email</option>
                        <option value="Outro">Outro</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div id="otherSourceDiv" style="display: none;">
                    <label for="otherSource" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Por favor, especifique:</label>
                    <input type="text" name="otherSource" id="otherSource" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500">
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label for="whatsappNumber" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Número de WhatsApp (opcional)</label>
                    <input type="tel" name="whatsappNumber" id="whatsappNumber" class="w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500" placeholder="Ex: +258 841234567">
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Fornecendo seu número, você concorda em receber atualizações e ofertas especiais por WhatsApp.</p>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-custom-gradient text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-md hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span>Enviar</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-paper-plane ml-2"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('sourceOfKnowledge').addEventListener('change', function() {
            var otherSourceDiv = document.getElementById('otherSourceDiv');
            if (this.value === 'Outro') {
                otherSourceDiv.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                otherSourceDiv.style.display = 'none';
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>